  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Not a Wise Hero archetype, Wisdom 13+, Level 2+</p><p>You have learned to act with efficiency rather than speed, carefully choosing the correct course of action.</p><ul><li><p>You gain Basic Equipment proficiency.</p></li><li><p>Choose one from Insight, Perception, Streetwise, and Survival. You gain proficiency in the chosen skill.</p></li><li><p>You gain 2 focus points. Your Focus recharges whenever you finish a short or long rest.</p></li><li><p>You can spend one focus point to reroll a failed Wisdom ability check. This may only be done once per ability check.</p></li><li><p>You can choose not to fall Prone when you Dive for Cover.</p></li></ul>",
